**Summary:** This documentation explains Amplitude's Engagement Matrix chart feature, which analyzes product feature engagement using a four-quadrant matrix view based on breadth (% active users) and frequency (times/days performed) metrics, supporting up to 100 events with options for DAU/WAU/MAU analysis and median/average sectioning.

